Author: TheGinkei
23.Text: I can't believe the asinine policies that most professors have to Pokedex distribution. I mean, all of their data gets leaked onto the web days after the latest updates and we're still expected to wait go through months waiting for a little plastic box for data that any two-bit trainer with a web connection could look up. Why is it that people want those things anyways?
